dtviz - dependency tree visualizer
==================================

Generate `graphviz`_ dot file based on dependecies from:

* pyproject.toml
* package.json


Requirements
------------

* python >=3.10


Install
-------

::

    $ pip install dtviz


Run
---

::

    $ dtviz --help


